DarkMouse::
She tried to run up and grab the unconsious kitty, but the fire was 
too hot. She stopped just a few feet from the fire wall. She turned 
and fired on the two dragons. "You flying lizards! That's our cat. Go 
find your own." as she fired on the two dragons again.
